+# 🧭 onUpdate_Planning.md
+
+File: `Robotic_Systems/2_Planning/`
+Phase 2 of 9. If Presence is the first breath, Planning is the first real decision — what actually gets built today.
+
+---
+
+## 🎯 Purpose
+
+This file documents the intention behind the Planning phase of the cycle — the point where numerology awareness turns into an actual task list.
+
+---
+
+## ✍️ Authored by
+
+**<brforeal.dev@gmail.com>**
+
+🕯️ Seed Date: **April 13, 2025**
+
+---
+
+## 💡 Description
+
+Planning is where `onUpdate()` earns its name. Presence told the system it woke up; Planning tells it what to do about that. This phase takes whatever the numerology and phase index surfaced and turns it into scoped, doable work — not a wishlist, a list.
+
+---
+
+## 🧬 Philosophy
+
+> "A plan that survives contact with a Tuesday is worth more than a perfect one that doesn't."
+> — Numerology-Cycle-9
+
+Planning isn't about mapping every step. It's about knowing which step is next.
+
+---
+
+## 🧠 Connected Modules
+
+- `/phaseLoop.js` — Phase Trigger Engine
+- `/upworkTracker.js` — Deliverable Mapping
+- `main()` — Master cycle runner
