@@ -0,0 +1,39 @@
+# ⚙️ onUpdate_Action.md
+
+File: `Robotic_Systems/3_Action/`
+Phase 3 of 9. This is the doing phase — where the plan stops being a document and starts being commits.
+
+---
+
+## 🎯 Purpose
+
+Documents the intention behind the Action phase: converting scoped work from Planning into real, shipped output.
+
+---
+
+## ✍️ Authored by
+
+**<brforeal.dev@gmail.com>**
+
+🕯️ Seed Date: **April 13, 2025**
+
+---
+
+## 💡 Description
+
+Action is the loudest phase and the shortest-lived one. No new decisions get made here — those already happened in Planning. This phase is execution only: write the code, run the script, close the loop. If Action starts second-guessing scope, that's a sign the cycle slipped back into Planning without saying so.
+
+---
+
+## 🧬 Philosophy
+
+> "Presence woke the system up. Planning gave it a target. Action is the only phase that leaves a diff."
+> — Numerology-Cycle-9
+
+---
+
+## 🧠 Connected Modules
+
+- `/phaseLoop.js` — Phase Trigger Engine
+- `/app.js` — Runtime execution
+- `/journalStore.js` — Snapshot persistence during active work
