+# 🛠️ onUpdate_Correction.md
+
+File: `Robotic_Systems/5_Correction/`
+Phase 5 of 9. The midpoint. Whatever Reflection flagged gets fixed here, before the cycle drifts any further off plan.
+
+---
+
+## 🎯 Purpose
+
+Documents the intention behind the Correction phase: closing the gap Reflection identified, without expanding scope while doing it.
+
+---
+
+## ✍️ Authored by
+
+**<brforeal.dev@gmail.com>**
+
+🕯️ Seed Date: **April 13, 2025**
+
+---
+
+## 💡 Description
+
+Correction is a scalpel, not a rebuild. It exists to fix the specific gap Reflection surfaced — a bug, a missed deliverable, a phase that fired wrong — and nothing beyond that. The temptation at the midpoint is to "just improve" something unrelated while you're in there. This phase resists that on purpose.
+
+---
+
+## 🧬 Philosophy
+
+> "Fix what Reflection pointed at. Nothing else earns your attention this phase."
+> — Numerology-Cycle-9
+
+---
+
+## 🧠 Connected Modules
+
+- `/phaseLoop.js` — Phase Trigger Engine
+- `/corpofFinality.js` — Phase state transitions
+- `/phaseJournal.js` — Logs the correction for the next Reflection pass
