+# 🌙 onUpdate_Rest.md
+
+File: `Robotic_Systems/7_Rest/`
+Phase 7 of 9. The system does nothing on purpose. That's the whole function.
+
+---
+
+## 🎯 Purpose
+
+Documents the intention behind the Rest phase: a deliberate non-action window built into the cycle, not a gap that happened by accident.
+
+---
+
+## ✍️ Authored by
+
+**<brforeal.dev@gmail.com>**
+
+🕯️ Seed Date: **April 13, 2025**
+
+---
+
+## 💡 Description
+
+Rest is easy to skip and expensive to skip. Six phases of Presence, Planning, Action, Reflection, Correction, and Connection compound fast — Rest is the phase that keeps the cycle from running the next round on fumes. No journal writes, no deliverable checks, no commits expected. If work happens during Rest, it wasn't Rest.
+
+---
+
+## 🧬 Philosophy
+
+> "The bridge needs a phase where nothing crosses it."
+> — Numerology-Cycle-9
+
+---
+
+## 🧠 Connected Modules
+
+- `/phaseLoop.js` — Phase Trigger Engine (idle pass-through)
+- None by design — this phase intentionally touches no active module
